        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Before Chrome can say anything, Kamui has already rushed off towards the Corrupted. He\\'s about to pull out his weapon when he turns around, as if suddenly reminded of something.'}"
